   <sense group="1" n="1" name="Adhere or bond physically, emotionally or socially" type="">
      <commentary>
        NOTE: Watch for adjectival uses of 'bound' as in 'The train is
        bound for London.' or 'He is bound to win the World Series.' Tag
        these as X. 
      </commentary>
      <examples>
     Do not be bound together with unbelievers.
     Will this wallpaper bind to the wall?
     The hydrogen binds with oxygen.
      </examples>
